## ✅ Your Code (for reference)

```js
useEffect(() => {
  let isMounted = true;

  const fetchData = async () => {
    const res = await fetch("/api/data");
    const data = await res.json();

    if (isMounted) {
      setData(data);
    }
  };

  fetchData();

  return () => {
    isMounted = false;
  };
}, []);
```

